Radioify Windows 11 Explorer integration
=======================================

This directory is generated by the build when
RADIOIFY_BUILD_WIN11_EXPLORER_INTEGRATION=ON.

Contents:
- radioify_explorer.dll: in-proc COM DLL for the Explorer command
- Package.appxmanifest: sparse package manifest scaffold
- README.txt: generated notes for this experimental lane

Current status:
- The DLL builds and exports the COM entry points.
- The install lane exists, but Explorer activation is still being proven.
- This directory is generated build output, not source-of-truth.

Useful commands:
- Build: .\build.ps1 -Static -Win11ExplorerIntegration
- Install: .\install_win11_explorer_integration.ps1
- Dry-run install: .\install_win11_explorer_integration.ps1 -WhatIf
- Uninstall: .\uninstall_win11_explorer_integration.ps1

Explorer activation log:
- %LOCALAPPDATA%\Radioify\win11-explorer.log

Command CLSID:
@RADIOIFY_WIN11_EXPLORER_COMMAND_CLSID@
